Error.sql:
SELECT 
                CONCAT(asal.nama_kandang, IFNULL(CONCAT(' - ', kdg_tujuan.nama_kandang), '')) AS nama_kandang,	
                CASE 
                    WHEN kartu_stock.penjualan_id IS NULL AND kartu_stock.distribusi_id IS NULL AND kartu_stock.tipe_transaksi = 'I' THEN
                        'Pembelian'
                    WHEN kartu_stock.penjualan_id IS NULL AND kartu_stock.distribusi_id IS NULL AND kartu_stock.tipe_transaksi = 'O' THEN
                        'Ayam Mati'
                    WHEN kartu_stock.penjualan_id IS NOT NULL AND kartu_stock.distribusi_id IS NULL THEN
                        'Penjualan'
                    WHEN kartu_stock.penjualan_id IS NULL AND kartu_stock.distribusi_id IS NOT NULL THEN
                        'Distribusi'
                    ELSE
                        '-'
                END AS tipe_trans,
                kartu_stock.tanggal,
                IFNULL(kartu_stock.penjualan_id, '-') AS penjualan_id,
                IFNULL(kartu_stock.distribusi_id, '-') AS distribusi_id,
                kartu_stock.quantity
            FROM 
                kartu_stock 
            INNER JOIN
                kandang AS asal ON asal.kandang_id = kartu_stock.kandang_id
            LEFT JOIN
                kandang AS kdg_tujuan ON kdg_tujuan.kandang_id = kartu_stock.tujuan
            WHERE
